<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>431</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. I kimuh, I kituok kit mau cheng!
 Pathien in hun veng zing henla;
 A huongsung ah hun veng bit hen,
 I kimuh, I kituok kit mau cheng!

[V2]
 I kimuh tuoh kit mau cheng,
 Lalpa Isu kengbul ah;
 Pathien in hun veng hen,
 I kimuh, I kituok kit mau cheng!

[V3]
 2. Pathien in hun umpih zing henla,
 A thalim nuoiah hun sel henla;
 Nicheng in nekding hun pie hen,
 I kimuh, I kituok kit mau cheng.

[V4]
 3. I kimuh, I kituok kit mau cheng,
 Damsung buoina na tuok tieng leh;
 A hehpih khutin hun tu hen,
 I kimuh, I kituok kit mau cheng.

[V5]
 4. I kimuh, I kituok kit mau cheng,
 A hehpihna'n hun veng zing hen;
 Thepna leh lauhum nawhmang hen,
 I kimuh, I kituok kit mau cheng.</lyrics>
<title>GOD BE WITH YOU!</title>
</song>